Baa (starting: Bolobog, Slarnath, Green Stuff)<br>
<br>
Phlouk (starting: Gremble, Jile, Muck <!--408-->Vinoc)<br>
<br>
Blygt (starting: Moob, Moss Quido, Swamp <!--409-->Weebo)<br>
<br>
Critters:<br>
Green Stuff x3<br>
Moob x3<br>
Bolobog x3<br>
Ainjer x3<br>
Zungg x3<br>
Treepsh x3<br>
Muck <!--408-->Vinoc x3<br>
Ooze <!--394-->Arboll x2<br>
Slarnath x3<br>
Moss Quido x1<br>
Gremble x1<br>
Jile x1<br>
<br>
Relics:<br>
Moss Pendant x2<br>
